media:group.media:title: My Big Brother Canada Experience..
media:group.media:description:
It was a dream come true being on the show, regardless of how short my time was.. The fact that thousands of people apply each year, and I got to be a part of this years cast.. Was truly a blessing.  Being the first transgender houseguest was an honour. I left my mark, and I'm so grateful to be a part of the Big Brother Canada family.
